Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(178,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H1F2AA3&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist Strikes Back!\NX Rider, Beware!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Intercepting one of GOD's secret messages, Jin Keisuke\Nfinally infiltrated their base: the Palace of Apollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But the formidable GOD Agency foiled Keisuke's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only is the X Rider challenged by a\Nfierce enemy in the Death God Chronos...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...But what are the two scientists working\Non beneath the Palace of Apollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who or what is laying on this operating table?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... won...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the GP. X Rider currently entering\Npalace. Initiate level one security precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Palace of Apollon is two hundred metres\Nunderground, its corridors labyrinthine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's capture is but a matter\Nof time. Now, begin the surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir, Supreme Commander. Initiating surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:04:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist, Chief of GOD's Secret Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only ever heard his name.\NBut what are we to do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell in battle with the X Rider.\NGOD cannot allow him to die like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD still has need of Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, he requires reconstructive surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. I'll infuse Apollo Geist's\Nbodily tissues with the strongest cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll upgrade Apollo Geist's mechanical parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I put my faith in your skills, doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can that accursed\NX Rider be hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My shoulder'll take an hour to heal...\Nand I need to stay hidden somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, seeing as I'm already here...\NMay as well take my time looking around...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had orders from the Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Have Kerberos initiate the Fire Plan while\Nwe contain the X Rider in the Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the tape with the Fire Plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD have all the bases covered...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We've thoroughly examined all\Nsixteen of the Palace's blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no hiding places left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider can't just have\Nvanished, and yet... Curse him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did you find him?\N-Negative!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Check rations, weapons,\Nand medical sectors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Medical's in surgery,\Nwe can't just barge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We certainly can!! The Palace's\Nsecurity is our only priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, you're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleeding...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's getting surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be what GOD\Nwants with the two doctors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I need to see this for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Geist Double Cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Magnum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, where's this\Nsurgery even happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Dr. Kawakami's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't see who it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A trail of blood! The X Rider\Ndid come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! Found me at last, did you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist's reconstructive\Nsurgery is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how does it feel to live again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Most refreshing! My thanks,\NSupreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct your thanks to the\Ndoctors Kawakami and Miyamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD provided these two with vast expenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that they did their jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Chief of Secret Police for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been reborn with powerful\Nnew mechanical parts installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us test them at once. Some\Ntraining will help you master them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I have a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A present...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is! We've got him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke... I see, so you're my\Npresent from the Supreme Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die until I've killed you! You\Nshould get used to the sight of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's test how quickly my\Nnew equipment takes your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Apollo Magnum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It fires three 22 calibre shells, enough\Nto scrap a heavy tank in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform into the X Rider! I get\Nno joy from fighting a human!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Set--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist! I'll fight you\Nwithout becoming the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Geist Double Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a whole day since Keisuke left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he isn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...No, no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana, the coffee--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Mako! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone just asked me\Nto give it to the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This job's tough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What, what? Something for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A present for the boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be from your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Show your elders some respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's that doll!!\N-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this one of GOD's dolls!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Watchdog of Hades, Kerberos, heed\Nthe Supreme Commander's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you need to get out of here! Hurry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until I've heard the\NSupreme Commander's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD!! Hey, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-We'd better hurry!\N-Right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist has GOD's enemy, the X Rider,\Nat his mercy in the Palace of Apollon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There is now no one on Earth capable of stopping the acts of GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:13:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Implement the Fire Plan at once! Reduce Tokyo to\Na sea of flames by overloading its electrical grid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the operation at Tachibana's coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Everything is in readiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As you heard, Tachibana's coffee shop\Nis now an asset of GOD's operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that! I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Boss!!\N-Hang in there, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that? Fifty thousand\Nvolts flow through my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-You won't get away with this!\N-Jin Keisuke will save us, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be seeing Jin Keisuke again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke... I'll wait for\Nyour wound to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But that will be the end of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything to stop\NGOD\N's Fire Plan like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll have to get out of here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist has ordered me to\Nassess Jin Keisuke's wound. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You--! But your wound--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One hour was all I needed.\NYou can thank Apollo Geist for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD does not brook failure!\NYou two must be executed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I brought you back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the time to flatter me!?\NWe have a security breach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Assemble all Palace\Nof Apollon personnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Elevators are off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The Supreme Commander\Nhas orders for Kerberos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work. Occupying Tachibana's coffee\Nshop will guarantee GOD's victory this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana's coffee shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They've occupied Tachibana's coffee\Nshop? Hold on a little longer, chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In ten minutes, every wire\Nin Tokyo will overload.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes, your lives will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up, Mako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that! Justice\Nhas to win in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Naive, so naive! There's nothing\Nstronger than evil in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait until the X Rider gets here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Jin Keisuke now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our security is flawless. Catching\Nhim is just a matter of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No attempts to contact the surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir! Just one agent who left with\Norders from the Supreme Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!! That was Jin Keisuke!\NGet after him at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Big Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you, didn't I? Your life\Nends once you become the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist, did you forget\Nthe X Rider defeated you once?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! I'm no longer\Nthe Apollo Geist I once was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how often you come back,\NApollo Geist is no match for the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this! Magnum Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Geist Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Apollo Geist, but I haven't\Ngot time to fight you. Another day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the Fire Plan's countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it really is no use this time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kerberos! The plan to burn\Ndown Tokyo is suspended!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspended!? No! I just--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order from GOD's\NSupreme Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That's not the Supreme\NCommander's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Who are you? Come out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-The X Rider!\N-X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast! How did you escape\Nthe Palace of Apollon!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-There, didn't I tell you?\N-He really did come!\N-Quick, save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools think the X Rider can\Nsave you? You're all going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, this guy's got fifty\Nthousand volts running through him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy that, X Rider?\NTouch my body all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn, Tokyo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whats going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I cut your little circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just have to kill you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me, Kerberos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is kill\Nyou and resume the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just get electrocuted\Nif I attack him directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Long Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty thousand volts isn't\Nsuch an advantage in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His greatest weapon turned\Nout to be his greatest weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:23:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Escaping the Palace of Apollon, the\NX Rider saved Tokyo from a fiery crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But the revived Apollo Geist will terrorise\Nthe X Rider with more challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep fighting, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The sounds of people in pain and sorrow\Ncarry on the wind through a quiet forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's monster Alseides has begun a\Nhorrible experiment to turn people into trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Scary! People are Turning into Trees!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider